#      DESCRIPTION:
#      ------------
#
#      This module implements the Dockerization of a MERN Backend/Server.
#
#
#      REFERENCES:
#      -----------
#
#      1. DOCKER Documentation
#         https://docs.docker.com/docker-hub/
